### Design Inspiration

This project is inspired by Nothing's design philosophy and aesthetic principles. While this is an open-source project, it is not officially affiliated with or endorsed by Nothing Technology Limited.

Nothing's design principles that inspire this project:

- Minimalism and functional design
- Technical precision and attention to detail
- Bold use of contrast and typography
- User-centered design approach

